{
  "stem": "8072.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't come to the Poland legally, because I didn't wait on the border for two days to get a permission to come in, because when we got off, we jumped the train and everything.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But since he took everything away from this other guy begged him, let him go, let him go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he let me go, and we went back to Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I told my sisters, I says-- and I really thought after surviving Auschwitz, Birkenau, Dachau, everything, that I'm going to get killed in Poland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told my sisters, I said, I don't know about you guys, if you're going to stay here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'm getting out of here, I'm getting out of here as fast as I can.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said, we want to leave, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took about a couple weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Give us a couple weeks, we'll liquidate it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all went back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Munich.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1949.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1949 I came to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in-- when I got to United States, was September.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Labor Day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- and I-- we landed in New Orleans, instead of New York because they told me-- because I came over on, through the [INAUDIBLE], you know, not by--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The relief--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't sponsored by anybody particular.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was going to come to Stockton.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So being I was coming to Stockton, so the ship landed in New Orleans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember very well that day because we were wearing that old [NON-ENGLISH] and the clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could see these river boats with with these people going on them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who was with you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was by myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By myself.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
